1
00:00:11,033 --> 00:00:15,067
<i>Remember this, I will never
call you my child ever again.</i>

2
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:20,967
<i>Because you don't deserve to be
my child or anyone else's.</i>

3
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:22,100
<i> What are you doing?</i>

4
00:00:24,667 --> 00:00:26,667
<i>- Mrs. Ligaya?
- Grandmother?</i>

5
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,567
<i> Grandmother!</i>

6
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:30,800
<i> Stop the wedding!</i>

7
00:00:30,933 --> 00:00:32,633
<i> Leave us alone, Emma!</i>

8
00:00:32,767 --> 00:00:35,400
<i>But the truth is, you're Olive!</i>

9
00:00:35,567 --> 00:00:38,900
<i> Admit it, Olive!</i>

10
00:01:17,233 --> 00:01:18,500
Mom.

11
00:01:18,633 --> 00:01:20,067
Mom, is what you said true?

12
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,767
She's Olive?

13
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,133
Yes, Dear.

14
00:01:23,267 --> 00:01:25,367
She's pretending to be Jade

15
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:28,400
so she can still do
everything she wants.

16
00:01:28,533 --> 00:01:29,967
All the evil things she does.

17
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:32,633
And so that she also
won't go back to jail!

18
00:01:32,767 --> 00:01:35,133
But the truth is,
she killed Jade.

19
00:01:35,267 --> 00:01:38,600
She killed my poor daughter.

20
00:01:38,733 --> 00:01:40,967
She killed her own sister.

21
00:01:42,567 --> 00:01:44,933
Is mom telling the truth?

22
00:01:45,067 --> 00:01:46,333
That you're Olive?

23
00:01:49,067 --> 00:01:51,133
You lied to us?

24
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,133
What are you talking about?

25
00:01:56,267 --> 00:01:58,367
Mom, what are you doing?

26
00:01:59,167 --> 00:02:00,900
This is me!

27
00:02:01,033 --> 00:02:03,333
I'm Jade!

28
00:02:03,467 --> 00:02:04,400
Mom!

29
00:02:04,533 --> 00:02:08,833
Olive has long been dead!
Please!

30
00:02:08,967 --> 00:02:12,633
Let her soul rest in peace!

31
00:02:12,767 --> 00:02:15,333
Stop denying it!

32
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,633
I'm not deaf,

33
00:02:16,767 --> 00:02:19,633
I heard everything you said

34
00:02:19,767 --> 00:02:21,633
the day you locked me up
in the room!

35
00:02:21,767 --> 00:02:24,233
You covered my mouth
so I wouldn't be able to scream!

36
00:02:24,367 --> 00:02:27,400
You let your henchman guard me
so I couldn't escape.

37
00:02:27,533 --> 00:02:28,667
And to keep everyone
from knowing the truth

38
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,700
that you're Olive!

39
00:02:30,833 --> 00:02:33,400
That's why you forcibly brought
me to the mental hospital

40
00:02:33,533 --> 00:02:34,867
and drove me insane.

41
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:42,067
So that explains why I feel
like you're Mommy Olive.

42
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,233
Because that's really you!

43
00:02:44,367 --> 00:02:46,200
- No.
- You're Mommy Olive!

44
00:02:46,333 --> 00:02:48,000
- No, no, no. Mookie, no.
- You're Mommy Olive.

45
00:02:48,167 --> 00:02:51,967
This is me. I'm your Mommy Jade!

46
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:55,233
They're just saying those things
to ruin me!

47
00:02:55,367 --> 00:02:56,333
Liar!

48
00:02:57,367 --> 00:02:58,733
You're a liar!

49
00:02:58,867 --> 00:03:02,333
Liar!

50
00:03:04,533 --> 00:03:06,733
Everyone knows

51
00:03:06,867 --> 00:03:14,200
that I still defended you even
after the evil things you did.

52
00:03:14,333 --> 00:03:16,600
I tolerated you.

53
00:03:16,733 --> 00:03:18,100
I tried to understand you

54
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:22,533
because I wanted to make amends
with you and Jade.

55
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:25,733
But you're a monster.
You're way out of line!

56
00:03:25,867 --> 00:03:27,733
You've become too evil.

57
00:03:27,867 --> 00:03:36,167
So I will never let you ruin
Emma and Mookie's lives.

58
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:39,167
So admit it, Olive!

59
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:41,533
I don't have anything
to confess!

60
00:03:42,567 --> 00:03:43,967
Because I'm not Olive!

61
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,367
I'm Jade!

62
00:03:46,767 --> 00:03:49,400
So, whether you want
to believe it or not,

63
00:03:49,533 --> 00:03:52,000
it's up to you!

64
00:03:52,133 --> 00:03:53,500
Won't you really confess?

65
00:03:53,633 --> 00:03:55,200
- I will prove it!
- Mom!

66
00:03:55,367 --> 00:03:56,233
Mom!

67
00:03:56,367 --> 00:03:57,267
Grandmother!

68
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,367
- Jade!
- Olive!

69
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,133
- Mom!
- Let's chase her!

70
00:03:59,267 --> 00:04:00,500
- Wait, wait.
- Mom, wait.

71
00:04:00,633 --> 00:04:01,433
I'll be right back.

72
00:04:01,567 --> 00:04:02,800
I'll follow Olive.

73
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:06,167
- Let's go there.
- Mom!

74
00:04:07,567 --> 00:04:08,833
Stay here.

75
00:04:15,933 --> 00:04:17,567
- Let go of me!
- Is it true?

76
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:20,100
- That you're Olive?
- No!

77
00:04:20,233 --> 00:04:21,533
Let me go, Danilo!

78
00:04:21,667 --> 00:04:22,867
Let me go!

79
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:27,033
Why are you trying to get away
if mom is lying?

80
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:32,367
Because I can see in your eyes
that you believe Ligaya!

81
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,767
That you're listening to Emma!

82
00:04:35,933 --> 00:04:40,133
You forgot about everything
I did for you and Mookie!

83
00:04:40,267 --> 00:04:43,667
I was the one with you
when Emma was away.

84
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,267
When Emma was fooling you!

85
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:49,767
I was with you, Danilo!

86
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:50,900
But now...

87
00:04:51,967 --> 00:04:53,900
are you ready to comfort me?

88
00:04:56,767 --> 00:04:59,500
Why can't you answer?

89
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:01,933
Because you've changed a lot!

90
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:05,033
So you can't blame me
for believing mom.

91
00:05:05,167 --> 00:05:09,067
You're only saying that because
you don't care about me!

92
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:13,267
Everything I did for you and
Mookie is nothing to you!

93
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,733
Because I'm so confused
right now!

94
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,333
Mom...

95
00:05:19,467 --> 00:05:21,233
are you sure you're okay?

96
00:05:25,167 --> 00:05:28,300
Don't worry about me, Dear.
I'm okay.

97
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,900
Emma...

98
00:05:34,633 --> 00:05:35,633
my dear.

99
00:05:39,767 --> 00:05:41,400
Please forgive me, Dear.

100
00:05:44,167 --> 00:05:47,233
Forgive me because the last time
we saw each other,

101
00:05:47,367 --> 00:05:49,367
things didn't go well.

102
00:05:50,533 --> 00:05:53,733
I wasn't there
when you needed me.

103
00:05:55,533 --> 00:05:57,067
I'm sorry, Dear.

104
00:05:59,033 --> 00:06:00,733
I wasn't there.

105
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:06,000
And forgive me for...

106
00:06:06,133 --> 00:06:08,600
putting Jade first.

107
00:06:08,767 --> 00:06:10,967
Who turns out to be Olive.

108
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,933
Because that time,

109
00:06:15,067 --> 00:06:18,333
Jade showed me pure kidness
when she was still alive.

110
00:06:18,467 --> 00:06:21,100
Her kindness is genuine.

111
00:06:21,233 --> 00:06:23,067
The real Jade's kindness
is real.

112
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,500
It was real.

113
00:06:25,633 --> 00:06:27,767
And Olive is so...

114
00:06:28,833 --> 00:06:32,267
Please forgive me, Dear.
I became weak.

115
00:06:33,433 --> 00:06:34,900
I'm sorry, Emma.

116
00:06:35,033 --> 00:06:36,700
I'm sorry, Dear.

117
00:06:40,033 --> 00:06:41,200
Mom.

118
00:06:41,367 --> 00:06:43,400
Mom, it's okay.

119
00:06:43,533 --> 00:06:45,567
I didn't hold grudges
against you.

120
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,167
I know that
you only longed for them.

121
00:06:50,433 --> 00:06:52,733
Yes, I got upset.

122
00:06:52,867 --> 00:06:57,900
But what matters is you're alive
and we're together.

123
00:07:14,933 --> 00:07:20,467
You're making me feel all
the pain I had when I was a kid.

124
00:07:22,367 --> 00:07:26,167
The pain of losing
my loved ones.

125
00:07:28,833 --> 00:07:32,367
That time, when my adoptive
parents never showed me love.

126
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:36,500
When my daughter died
and left me.

127
00:07:36,633 --> 00:07:39,467
Maria Angela.

128
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:44,333
So you can't blame me
if I got interested in Mookie.

129
00:07:44,467 --> 00:07:48,700
You can't blame me
for doing that.

130
00:07:50,533 --> 00:07:52,633
You got interested in Mookie?

131
00:07:56,767 --> 00:07:58,567
You really are Olive!

132
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:01,000
- Danilo!
- Damn you!

133
00:08:01,133 --> 00:08:03,733
You're Olive!
You took our daughter!

134
00:08:04,067 --> 00:08:04,533
- You're Olive!
- Danilo!

135
00:08:04,667 --> 00:08:06,500
You took our daughter!

136
00:08:08,433 --> 00:08:11,167
Monster!

137
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,633
- Mom.
- Mom.

138
00:08:12,767 --> 00:08:14,733
I think that's dad.

139
00:08:14,867 --> 00:08:15,833
It seems like things
are getting physical

140
00:08:15,967 --> 00:08:17,167
between him and Mommy Olive.

141
00:08:18,733 --> 00:08:19,867
Mom, Mom.

142
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,867
Stay here. Stay here, okay?

143
00:08:22,033 --> 00:08:22,933
Zayn,

144
00:08:23,067 --> 00:08:24,500
- please look after my mom.
- Yes, I will.

145
00:08:24,633 --> 00:08:25,900
- Mom, we'll take care of it.
- Let's go, Mom.

146
00:08:26,033 --> 00:08:26,633
Come on.

147
00:08:26,767 --> 00:08:28,267
Emma, be safe.

148
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,700
Let go of me.

149
00:08:39,267 --> 00:08:40,033
Dan!

150
00:08:42,233 --> 00:08:43,733
Come back here!

151
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,233
I said come back here!

152
00:08:53,367 --> 00:08:54,033
Olive!

153
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:56,067
What's wrong with you!

154
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,833
Let me go!

155
00:08:57,967 --> 00:08:59,633
I said let me go!

156
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,900
Mom told me everything.

157
00:09:04,167 --> 00:09:06,300
How dare you. You, monster!

158
00:09:06,433 --> 00:09:07,400
You're wanted by the police,

159
00:09:07,533 --> 00:09:09,067
that's why you pretended
to be Jade.

160
00:09:09,367 --> 00:09:14,133
But no matter how you pretend,
your true colors still come out!

161
00:09:14,267 --> 00:09:15,333
Snake skin!

162
00:09:15,467 --> 00:09:17,300
Call me a snake if you want!

163
00:09:18,033 --> 00:09:20,000
What do you call yourselves?

164
00:09:20,133 --> 00:09:21,200
Dumb!

165
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,833
Emma!

166
00:09:25,967 --> 00:09:27,467
- That's enough!
- Mom!

167
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,733
Emma, stop!

168
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,067
What now?

169
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:33,467
Your demon-like laughter
is hurting my ears!

170
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,100
- Mom!
- I'll make sure

171
00:09:36,233 --> 00:09:38,267
that you can never
have an evil laugh!

172
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,300
Let go of me!

173
00:09:40,433 --> 00:09:42,700
Let go of me!

174
00:09:42,833 --> 00:09:46,033
I know you're a bad person.

175
00:09:46,167 --> 00:09:47,333
But I never thought

176
00:09:47,467 --> 00:09:51,300
you could do worse than what
you did to me and my daughter!

177
00:09:51,433 --> 00:09:55,500
After giving my daughter
all sorts of medicines,

178
00:09:55,633 --> 00:09:57,533
you drove me insane
in Havenwood.

179
00:09:57,667 --> 00:10:02,300
You hurt and treated mom
like an animal!

180
00:10:02,467 --> 00:10:06,133
And you killed Jade,
your twin sister,

181
00:10:06,267 --> 00:10:08,900
just like that!

182
00:10:09,033 --> 00:10:10,533
Piece of cake.

183
00:10:10,667 --> 00:10:12,733
So if I were you, Emma,

184
00:10:12,867 --> 00:10:14,333
I'd be scared.

185
00:10:14,467 --> 00:10:19,167
If I could kill my own twin,
what do you think I'd do to you?

186
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,933
Stop!

187
00:10:22,733 --> 00:10:24,833
Do you think
you can outsmart me?

188
00:10:26,433 --> 00:10:27,700
Dan!

189
00:10:27,833 --> 00:10:29,367
Mookie!

190
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,500
Dan!

191
00:10:30,633 --> 00:10:31,767
Mookie!

192
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:34,200
Dan, she might do something
to Mookie!

193
00:10:34,367 --> 00:10:35,733
Mommy, stop!

194
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:38,400
Mookie?

195
00:10:38,533 --> 00:10:40,033
Mommy, stop it already.

196
00:10:42,533 --> 00:10:43,833
Mookie...

197
00:10:43,967 --> 00:10:45,333
Mookie, did you come here

198
00:10:45,467 --> 00:10:48,833
because you realized
you want to be with me?

199
00:10:48,967 --> 00:10:51,567
Do you want to be with me
more than Emma?

200
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,967
Mookie!

201
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,500
Mookie!

202
00:10:55,633 --> 00:10:56,600
No!

203
00:10:56,733 --> 00:11:01,033
I realized you really
are a murderer.

204
00:11:01,167 --> 00:11:02,700
I used to feel sorry for you

205
00:11:02,833 --> 00:11:04,467
because I thought
you were just lonely.

206
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:07,333
That's why you were hurting
other people.

207
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,667
But I was wrong.

208
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:12,333
You're not just sad, Mommy.

209
00:11:13,967 --> 00:11:15,967
You're a demon.

210
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:17,400
Crazy.

211
00:11:17,533 --> 00:11:19,067
You're crazy, Mommy!

212
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:21,700
- Crazy!
- How dare you!

213
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:26,500
How dare you speak to me
that way!

214
00:11:26,633 --> 00:11:28,200
Come with me!

215
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,667
Come with me!

216
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,367
I'm your family!

217
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:32,967
You're only mine!

218
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,900
I'm not coming with you!

219
00:11:35,033 --> 00:11:37,300
- You should see a doctor!
- No!

220
00:11:37,433 --> 00:11:39,333
So you can stop hurting

221
00:11:39,467 --> 00:11:40,733
- other people.
- No!

222
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:43,733
No, Mookie! You're mine!

223
00:11:43,867 --> 00:11:47,033
No! So you can stop messing
with our family!

224
00:11:47,167 --> 00:11:48,300
Mookie!

225
00:11:48,433 --> 00:11:49,633
Mookie, no!

226
00:11:49,767 --> 00:11:50,733
No!

227
00:11:52,033 --> 00:11:53,233
Mookie!

228
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:02,100
What if something bad
is already happening to them?

229
00:12:02,233 --> 00:12:03,267
Zayn,

230
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,600
- what if we follow them?
- Oh, no.

231
00:12:05,733 --> 00:12:07,133
Please don't.

232
00:12:07,267 --> 00:12:09,167
It's dangerous. Something bad
might happen to you.

233
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:11,767
If it's okay with you,
I'll go and check on them.

234
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:13,633
Promise me
that you won't go anywhere.

235
00:12:13,767 --> 00:12:15,233
Please stay here.

236
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,367
Okay.

237
00:12:22,333 --> 00:12:24,133
- Mookie.
- Mookie!

238
00:12:24,267 --> 00:12:25,100
Mookie, dear!

239
00:12:25,233 --> 00:12:26,433
Mookie!

240
00:12:26,567 --> 00:12:29,567
Dan, what happened to Mookie?

241
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:30,833
Dan, hurry up!

242
00:12:30,967 --> 00:12:32,667
Mookie, Mookie!

243
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,400
- Zayn.
- What happened to Mookie?

244
00:12:34,533 --> 00:12:36,200
We need to bring her
to the hospital.

245
00:12:36,333 --> 00:12:37,500
- Use my car.
- Let's go.

246
00:12:37,633 --> 00:12:39,233
- Thank you, Zayn.
- Please look after my mom.

247
00:12:39,367 --> 00:12:40,667
Come on, let's go!

248
00:12:44,333 --> 00:12:45,467
Mookie.

249
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,633
Mookie!

250
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,067
Ma'am Jade?

251
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,633
- Give me the car keys. Hurry!
- Why? Where are you going?

252
00:12:57,767 --> 00:12:59,100
Just give it to me!

253
00:12:59,233 --> 00:13:02,000
- Get out of my way!
- Ma'am Jade, I'll get lectured!

254
00:13:02,133 --> 00:13:04,533
I'll get fired, Ma'am!

255
00:13:04,667 --> 00:13:06,100
Ma'am Jade!

256
00:13:06,233 --> 00:13:07,200
Ma'am!

257
00:13:09,167 --> 00:13:10,433
I'm sorry, Mrs. Ligaya.

258
00:13:10,567 --> 00:13:13,433
I wasn't able to catch
Aunt Olive.

259
00:13:13,567 --> 00:13:15,367
But, they said she ran away

260
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:19,700
when she saw Uncle Danilo and
Aunt Emma taking care of Mookie.

261
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,900
What?

262
00:13:21,033 --> 00:13:22,733
She escaped again?

263
00:13:26,867 --> 00:13:28,867
Lord, what is this?

264
00:13:30,700 --> 00:13:34,100
The problems just keep coming.
There's no end in sight.

265
00:13:35,633 --> 00:13:39,200
Ma'am, is Ms. Caparas
with someone else?

266
00:13:39,333 --> 00:13:40,500
Does she have an accomplice?

267
00:13:40,633 --> 00:13:44,033
I don't know. As for me, I don't
trust any of Olive's lackeys.

268
00:13:44,833 --> 00:13:46,367
Logan, too!

269
00:13:47,433 --> 00:13:49,167
He likes Emma!

270
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:52,333
- Vicente, track Logan.
- Yes, Sir.

271
00:13:52,467 --> 00:13:54,900
And you, ask the guests around.

272
00:13:57,700 --> 00:14:00,233
Do you have anything else to say
about Logan?

273
00:14:03,333 --> 00:14:04,733
What are you going to do now?

274
00:14:04,867 --> 00:14:07,167
You hurt your daughter again.

275
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:09,533
You almost killed Mookie again.

276
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,367
No.

277
00:14:13,767 --> 00:14:15,200
I didn't mean it.

278
00:14:16,433 --> 00:14:19,767
I didn't want to hurt her,
but she doesn't want me anymore.

279
00:14:21,233 --> 00:14:23,233
She thinks I'm evil.

280
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,800
Then show her that you're
the only one she needs.

281
00:14:32,267 --> 00:14:34,367
That you're her savior.

282
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:38,100
That she needs you to live
and get better.

283
00:14:47,967 --> 00:14:49,167
<i> Hello, Ma'am?</i>

284
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,667
Hello.

285
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,433
I need you to do something
for me.

286
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:55,700
Don't forget my gun.

287
00:14:55,833 --> 00:14:57,767
But be quick...

288
00:14:57,900 --> 00:15:00,900
because Mookie can't die.

289
00:15:01,033 --> 00:15:02,400
She needs me.

290
00:15:02,567 --> 00:15:05,167
My daughter needs me to live.

291
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,167
And I'm the only one
who can cure her.

292
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:10,067
I'm the only one
who can help her.

293
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,500
No one else.

294
00:15:11,633 --> 00:15:13,100
So hurry up!

295
00:15:25,433 --> 00:15:26,833
Hello, Marco?

296
00:15:26,967 --> 00:15:28,933
Have you already taken care
of what I asked you to fix?

297
00:15:33,567 --> 00:15:34,567
Okay, good.

298
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,033
Very good.

299
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,167
Very good.

300
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:43,667
Why did we lose sight of them?

301
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:45,167
Where are they?

302
00:15:47,333 --> 00:15:48,833
Hurry up!

303
00:15:51,933 --> 00:15:52,767
Dan.

304
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:54,933
Dan, why is Mookie
still unconscious?

305
00:15:55,067 --> 00:15:57,233
There's no blood in her head.

306
00:15:58,767 --> 00:16:00,533
Mookie.

307
00:16:00,667 --> 00:16:02,800
Mookie, dear.

308
00:16:02,933 --> 00:16:06,033
- Please wake up.
- This is my fault.

309
00:16:06,167 --> 00:16:08,833
I let Jade be part of our lives.

310
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,400
I mean Olive.

311
00:16:11,733 --> 00:16:13,567
I'm a worthless husband
and father.

312
00:16:15,133 --> 00:16:17,667
We're all victims of Olive.

313
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,967
She took advantage
of our weaknesses.

314
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:22,133
She's so evil.

315
00:16:28,167 --> 00:16:29,167
Emma...

316
00:16:30,567 --> 00:16:32,633
- someone's following us.
- Dan?

317
00:16:41,667 --> 00:16:42,967
Dan.

318
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:44,133
Dan!

319
00:16:47,067 --> 00:16:48,800
- The brake is not working!
- What?

320
00:16:52,167 --> 00:16:53,233
Mookie.

321
00:17:16,467 --> 00:17:17,433
Mom?

322
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,333
Dad?

323
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:31,533
Help!

324
00:17:33,867 --> 00:17:36,400
Please help us!

325
00:17:39,933 --> 00:17:41,400
- Mrs. Ligaya!
- Ligaya!

326
00:17:41,533 --> 00:17:42,600
BFF!

327
00:17:44,367 --> 00:17:46,367
Mrs. Ligaya, sorry for coming
so late.

328
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:48,500
Are you okay?

329
00:17:48,667 --> 00:17:50,433
We didn't catch anything.

330
00:17:50,567 --> 00:17:52,367
Everything was over.

331
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:57,567
How are you, friend?

332
00:17:57,700 --> 00:18:01,767
- You need to see a doctor.
- Yes!

333
00:18:02,233 --> 00:18:04,133
No.

334
00:18:04,267 --> 00:18:06,133
I don't need a hospital.

335
00:18:07,233 --> 00:18:10,833
All I need
is to see Emma and Mookie.

336
00:18:10,967 --> 00:18:14,700
I need to make sure
that my family's safe.

337
00:18:17,333 --> 00:18:21,100
- Are you sure?
- Especially now!

338
00:18:21,233 --> 00:18:25,067
Zayn told me
that Olive escaped again.

339
00:18:25,667 --> 00:18:26,800
What?

340
00:18:26,933 --> 00:18:28,133
Oh my God.

341
00:18:40,233 --> 00:18:43,800
Help. Help us, please!

342
00:18:54,067 --> 00:18:55,300
- Come on, let's go.
- Mister!

343
00:18:55,467 --> 00:18:57,200
- Go get the girl.
- Hurry up.

344
00:18:57,333 --> 00:18:59,033
Mister! Miss!

345
00:18:59,167 --> 00:19:04,533
Help us, please. Help!
Help us, Mister.

346
00:19:04,667 --> 00:19:06,100
Mister.

347
00:19:06,233 --> 00:19:07,300
Mister.

348
00:19:09,433 --> 00:19:10,467
Mister.

349
00:19:11,533 --> 00:19:16,267
My mom and dad are still there.
Please help them.

350
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,433
Mookie?

351
00:19:25,567 --> 00:19:26,367
Dan?

352
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:28,233
Miss! Miss!

353
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:31,067
Miss, where's my daughter?

354
00:19:39,767 --> 00:19:41,033
Olive?

355
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,967
Give me back my daughter!

356
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:45,233
Mookie!

357
00:19:51,367 --> 00:19:55,300
Why would I give her back to you
when she's mine to begin with?

358
00:19:55,433 --> 00:19:57,200
You're the one
who stole from me, Emma.

359
00:19:57,333 --> 00:19:59,100
Not the other way around!

360
00:19:59,233 --> 00:20:01,533
So what you deserve is to...

361
00:20:02,267 --> 00:20:03,500
die!

362
00:20:05,533 --> 00:20:08,100
Go ahead! I dare you.

363
00:20:08,233 --> 00:20:10,200
Mister, thank you.

364
00:20:10,333 --> 00:20:14,100
My mom and dad
are still in the car, Mister.

365
00:20:14,233 --> 00:20:15,200
Your mom and dad?

366
00:20:15,333 --> 00:20:17,667
They're not part of this.

367
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:19,800
Mister, what are you doing
to me?

368
00:20:19,933 --> 00:20:22,233
- Stay still!
- Mister!

369
00:20:24,667 --> 00:20:26,367
Call for help! Hurry!

370
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:28,400
- Olive!
- Logan!

371
00:20:28,533 --> 00:20:29,833
Olive!

372
00:20:29,967 --> 00:20:32,400
- That's enough!
- Try to take one more step.

373
00:20:32,533 --> 00:20:33,933
Try to take one more step,
Logan!

374
00:20:34,067 --> 00:20:35,000
I'll pull the trigger!

375
00:20:35,167 --> 00:20:37,600
Let it end in death, if it must!

376
00:20:37,733 --> 00:20:39,533
I will take my daughter back!

377
00:20:39,667 --> 00:20:43,067
- I said stop!
- Who told you to get involved?

378
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,000
Olive!

379
00:20:45,133 --> 00:20:46,633
Mom! Mom!

380
00:20:46,767 --> 00:20:48,433
Help! Mom!

381
00:20:48,567 --> 00:20:51,233
I'll keep getting her from you!

382
00:20:51,367 --> 00:20:53,700
So if I were you, Emma,
I'd give up.

383
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:57,067
Because I'll do everything
for Mookie!

384
00:20:59,533 --> 00:21:00,633
Stop!

385
00:21:00,767 --> 00:21:04,067
I'll kill everyone who gets
in the way of my plans!

386
00:21:05,433 --> 00:21:06,533
Stop!

387
00:21:06,667 --> 00:21:08,100
I'll pull the trigger.

388
00:21:08,267 --> 00:21:09,867
Why are you getting involved
as well?

389
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,000
Stop it!

390
00:21:13,933 --> 00:21:15,000
Stop!

391
00:21:27,633 --> 00:21:28,600
Logan?

392
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:32,267
Logan?

393
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,367
Logan!

394
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,633
Logan!

395
00:21:34,767 --> 00:21:35,767
Logan!

396
00:21:37,733 --> 00:21:39,833
Lucky you, Emma.

397
00:21:39,967 --> 00:21:42,967
Logan took the bullet
that was meant for you.

398
00:21:45,467 --> 00:21:46,433
Logan.

399
00:21:46,567 --> 00:21:47,567
Logan!

400
00:21:50,167 --> 00:21:51,233
Olive!

401
00:21:51,367 --> 00:21:52,400
Mookie!

402
00:21:52,533 --> 00:21:53,767
Mookie!

403
00:21:53,900 --> 00:21:54,700
Mookie!

404
00:21:55,867 --> 00:21:57,267
Mookie! Mookie!

405
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,933
Mookie!

406
00:22:02,067 --> 00:22:03,567
Mookie!

407
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:05,100
Mookie!

408
00:22:05,233 --> 00:22:06,567
Mookie!

409
00:22:18,100 --> 00:22:19,133
Logan!

410
00:22:19,267 --> 00:22:20,067
Logan!

411
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:21,400
Logan!

412
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,867
Why did you do that?

413
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:28,733
It hurts, Emma.

414
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,300
Why?

415
00:22:34,367 --> 00:22:35,633
Because I love you.

416
00:22:45,633 --> 00:22:46,967
Please forgive me.

417
00:22:50,233 --> 00:22:53,233
I did all that...

418
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:56,167
because of you.

419
00:22:57,300 --> 00:22:58,833
All my life...

420
00:23:01,133 --> 00:23:03,233
people have always left me.

421
00:23:04,767 --> 00:23:07,267
No one ever loves me.

422
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:10,600
Someone will love you.

423
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:14,567
But you're the one I love.

424
00:23:18,433 --> 00:23:19,100
It's okay...

425
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,800
because I know...

426
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:28,500
I know you're happy with Danilo.

427
00:23:28,633 --> 00:23:30,833
So it's okay for me to die.

428
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,233
So you can be...

429
00:23:35,033 --> 00:23:36,067
together...

430
00:23:37,533 --> 00:23:39,067
as a family.

431
00:23:40,733 --> 00:23:41,967
The three of you.

432
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,233
Logan, please forgive me

433
00:23:45,367 --> 00:23:49,667
if I can't reciprocate
your love.

434
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,167
Forgive me.

435
00:23:55,867 --> 00:23:57,900
You don't have to ask
for forgiveness.

436
00:24:00,367 --> 00:24:02,133
It's enough for me.

437
00:24:02,267 --> 00:24:04,867
The love you gave me...

438
00:24:05,900 --> 00:24:07,267
when we were still together.

439
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:12,833
Thank you, Emma.

440
00:24:12,967 --> 00:24:15,067
Dan! Dan, ask for help.

441
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,333
Call an ambulance.

442
00:24:16,467 --> 00:24:17,533
Hurry!

443
00:24:17,667 --> 00:24:18,600
Dan!

444
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,100
Logan?

445
00:24:30,233 --> 00:24:31,800
Logan!

446
00:24:31,933 --> 00:24:32,933
Dan!

447
00:24:51,233 --> 00:24:52,100
Hello, Zayn?

448
00:24:52,233 --> 00:24:53,367
<i> Aunt Emma!</i>

449
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,667
Miss Astrid told us
where Mookie is.

450
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,433
Here's the memaristol.

451
00:24:57,567 --> 00:24:58,633
Perfect.

452
00:24:58,767 --> 00:25:00,633
But I did some research.

453
00:25:00,767 --> 00:25:03,133
They say it erases memories.

454
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:04,233
Don't tell me...

455
00:25:04,367 --> 00:25:05,800
Yup.

456
00:25:05,933 --> 00:25:06,767
It's for Mookie.

457
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:08,200
No!

458
00:25:08,333 --> 00:25:12,467
Olive won't stop until
she ruins our family.

459
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:16,500
Dan, let's work together
for Mookie.
